1. Moj *direktor* ne voli kad kasnim na posao. (My *director* doesn't like it when I'm late for work.)
2. Poslao sam mejl *direktoru* kompanije sa predlogom za poboljšanje poslovanja. (I sent an email to the *company director* with a proposal to improve business.)
3. *Direktor* je dao odobrenje za kupovinu novog računara. (The *director* approved the purchase of a new computer.)
4. Upravo sam čuo da će *direktor* kompanije da se penzioniše krajem godine. (I just heard that the *company director* is going to retire at the end of the year.)
5. Svi zaposleni su bili pozvani na sastanak sa *direktorom*. (All employees were invited to a meeting with the *director*.)
6. Šef odeljenja je podneo ostavku i sada tražimo novog *direktora*. (The department manager resigned and now we are looking for a new *director*.)
7. *Direktoru* je potrebna nova sekretarica koja će mu pomagati u svakodnevnom radu. (The *director* needs a new secretary to assist him in his daily work.)
8. Naša kompanija ima pet *direktora* koji se bave različitim aspektima poslovanja. (Our company has five *directors* who deal with different aspects of business.)
9. Zaposleni su bili veoma iznenađeni kada su videli *direktora* u restoranu u sred radnog vremena. (The employees were very surprised when they saw the *director* in the restaurant during working hours.)
10. Ova odluka će biti doneta na sastanku *direktora* koji je zakazan za sutra. (This decision will be made at the *directors' meeting* scheduled for tomorrow.)